room_title: Escape room "The Omega Code" by The Code and Key Escape Rooms in Bloomington (IN)
review: I really enjoyed this escape room due to the fact that it is private bookings only. It makes for a more intimate and fun experience with those in your group. It was challenging and lots of fun. I would recommend for all ages. The people working were very nice, friendly, and helpful! I would definitely go back.

room_title: Escape room "The Omega Code" by The Code and Key Escape Rooms in Bloomington (IN)
review: Had a great time with 3 other people all with varying experiences with puzzles and ciphers, and some with no experience. It was challenging and entertaining. We will be back when the other room is ready!

room_title: Escape room "The Omega Code" by The Code and Key Escape Rooms in Bloomington (IN)
review: We had an awesome time with our group (8), there were a few moments that blew our minds and made for a very memorable experience! I can't wait to try the next room that is coming out soon!
